caption: Table 1: Dataset statistics
description: The table lists eight datasets used in the paper's empirical evaluation.  For each dataset, the number of samples and the number of features are provided.  The datasets include both real-world datasets (e.g., MNIST, Fashion-MNIST, Wine) and a synthetic dataset (twomoons).  Some datasets have been pre-processed (e.g., dimensionality reduction for MNIST and Fashion-MNIST).
